<TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=120 BGCOLOR="#DDDDDD"><FONT CLASS=GraphicCaption>"These guys know something about slow news days, believe you me."</FONT></TD>
<TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><IMG SRC="images/spacer.gif"></TD>
